  "prompt": "Why doesn't Quora show my question to anyone?",
  "response": "If your question isn't being shown on Quora, there could be several reasons for this. Here are some common possibilities:\n\n### 1. **Pending Moderation**\n   - Quora may be reviewing your question to ensure it complies with their guidelines. This process can take some time, especially if the question touches on sensitive topics.\n\n### 2. **Question Violates Guidelines**\n   - If your question includes content that violates Quora's policies (e.g., offensive language, spam, or personal attacks), it may be removed or not shown to others.\n\n### 3. **Low Quality or Vague**\n   - Quora may deem your question too vague, unclear, or irrelevant to the community. Questions that lack context or specificity are less likely to be distributed.\n\n### 4. **Duplicate Question**\n   - If your question is similar to one that\u2019s already been asked, Quora may merge it with the existing question or not display it to avoid repetition.\n\n### 5. **Technical Issues**\n   - There could be a temporary glitch or bug preventing your question from being displayed. Try refreshing the page or posting it again.\n\n### 6. **Account Restrictions**\n   - If your account has been flagged for violating Quora's policies, your content may be limited or hidden from others.\n\n### 7. **Algorithmic Filtering**\n   - Quora\u2019s algorithm may not consider your question relevant enough to share widely, especially if it\u2019s too niche or lacks engagement potential.\n\n### 8. **Private or Anonymous Posting**\n   - If you posted the question anonymously or set it to private, it won\u2019t be visible to the general audience.\n\n### What You Can Do:\n   - **Check Your Notifications:** Quora may notify you if your question was removed or needs editing.\n   - **Rephrase Your Question:** Ensure it\u2019s clear, specific, and follows Quora\u2019s guidelines.\n   - **Contact Quora Support:** If you believe your question was unfairly removed, you can reach out to Quora\u2019s support team for clarification.\n\nBy addressing these potential issues, you can increase the likelihood of your question being shown and answered by the Quora community.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
